creator: zilla@kayari.org
text:
The man pages for ab(8) and apachectl(8) incorrectly claim to be in section 1 of
the manual.

"man -w apachectl" gives:
    /usr/share/man/man8/apachectl.8.gz

but "man apachectl" gives:

apachectl(1)                                         apachectl(1)

NAME
       apachectl - Apache HTTP server control interface

I'll attach a patch to change this...

creator: zilla@kayari.org
text:
Created attachment 9314
Change section number in ab and apachectl man pages
